Subject: Re: [T2] oil leaking pretty bad suddenly

Oil Pressure sender gone bad.  Pull the engine cover and look straight 
down in front of the distributor.  See the wire?  Remove it.  Remove 
rubber boot and use a 15/16" socket to remove the sender.  Screw a new 
one in and your oil leak is cured.

Jim
